WEBVTT

1
00:00:07.340 --> 00:00:09.342
[distant tapping]

2
00:00:11.011 --> 00:00:13.138
[spectral shriek]

3
00:00:15.390 --> 00:00:17.392
[Gu-cheon grunting]

4
00:00:17.475 --> 00:00:19.477
