5
00:00:21.104 --> 00:00:22.272
[woman screams]

6
00:00:25.984 --> 00:00:27.736
[pond spirit shrieks]

7
00:00:28.903 --> 00:00:30.155
[Gu-cheon grunts]

8
00:00:31.406 --> 00:00:32.866
[panting]

9
00:00:35.243 --> 00:00:36.494
[women screaming]

10
00:00:36.578 --> 00:00:38.830
