13
00:00:52.052 --> 00:00:54.054
[panting]

14
00:00:58.475 --> 00:01:00.477
[music swells]

15
00:01:00.560 --> 00:01:02.645
-[music subsides]
-[breathing heavily]

16
00:01:02.729 --> 00:01:03.897
Now.

17
00:01:06.524 --> 00:01:08.318
Let us make a deal with each other.

18
00:01:11.321 --> 00:01:14.532
I will give you half of my yang energy.
and in returnâ€¦

19
00:01:16.576 --> 00:01:18.411
your help is all I require.

20
00:01:18.495 --> 00:01:20.497
[breathing heavily]

21
00:01:25.251 --> 00:01:26.377
[gasping]

22
00:01:28.296 --> 00:01:30.298
