25
00:01:40.350 --> 00:01:42.393
[sinister music playing]

26
00:01:42.477 --> 00:01:45.021
[spectral growling]

27
00:01:45.105 --> 00:01:47.107
[spectral screaming]

28
00:01:48.608 --> 00:01:51.361
-[spectral screaming]
-[squelching]

29
00:01:58.535 --> 00:01:59.869
[growling]

30
00:02:10.004 --> 00:02:11.256
Shit.

31
00:02:18.346 --> 00:02:20.348
[spectral screaming]

32
00:02:20.431 --> 00:02:22.433
[tense dramatic music resumes]

33
00:02:24.978 --> 00:02:26.563
[spectral screaming]

34
00:02:44.706 --> 00:02:45.707
[Gu-cheon grunts]

35
00:02:49.919 --> 00:02:53.631
At this rate. your soul will be destroyed.

36
00:02:56.342 --> 00:02:58.636
