38
00:03:13.443 --> 00:03:15.445
[spectral screaming]

39
00:03:24.954 --> 00:03:27.040
-[snarling]
-[Gu-cheon grunts]

40
00:03:32.045 --> 00:03:33.463
[Gu-cheon straining]

41
00:03:37.508 --> 00:03:39.510
[snarls]

42
00:03:42.222 --> 00:03:44.682
[Gu-cheon grunting in pain]

43
00:03:50.188 --> 00:03:52.023
If I lose all my yang energy.

44
00:03:53.441 --> 00:03:54.901
then I will die too.

45
00:03:54.984 --> 00:03:57.612
[grunting. straining]

46
00:03:58.238 --> 00:03:59.322
[squelching]

47
00:04:01.532 --> 00:04:02.659
[gasps. grunts]

48
00:04:04.994 --> 00:04:07.705
-[Saeng-gang grunting]
-[epic percussive music playing]

49
00:04:11.042 --> 00:04:12.293
[both grunt]

50
00:04:13.836 --> 00:04:15.588
[gasping]

51
00:04:16.297 --> 00:04:17.298
[snarls]

52
00:04:20.969 --> 00:04:23.221
-[Gu-cheon grunts]
-[snarling]

53
00:04:23.846 --> 00:04:26.683
[Gu-cheon screaming]

54
00:04:26.766 --> 00:04:29.143
[straining]

55
00:04:33.606 --> 00:04:34.607
[gasps]

56
00:04:37.652 --> 00:04:39.570
[screaming]

57
00:04:40.738 --> 00:04:43.283
[straining]

58
00:04:45.159 --> 00:04:47.662
[grunting]

59
00:04:48.746 --> 00:04:50.790
[gasping. grunts]

60
00:04:59.382 --> 00:05:01.384
[gasping]

61
00:05:13.980 --> 00:05:16.441
[groaning]

62
00:05:17.692 --> 00:05:19.027
I told you not toâ€¦

63
00:05:19.110 --> 00:05:21.612
[grunts. groans]

64
00:05:27.702 --> 00:05:29.704
[music intensifies]

65
00:05:31.622 --> 00:05:36.544
THE EAST PALACE

66
00:05:36.627 --> 00:05:38.629
[music fades]

67
00:05:43.092 --> 00:05:44.177
Are you all right?

68
00:05:47.138 --> 00:05:48.973
