69
00:05:50.058 --> 00:05:52.226
You were the one who saved him.
were you not?

70
00:05:52.810 --> 00:05:56.439
[clears throat] What's important is.
why did you pull the rope?

71
00:05:58.024 --> 00:05:59.525
Because I heard the bell stop ringing.

72
00:05:59.609 --> 00:06:02.236
and I thought that you might
be in danger or something.

73
00:06:03.654 --> 00:06:04.572
Was I interrupting?

74
00:06:05.198 --> 00:06:07.033
I thought I told you loud and clear before

75
00:06:07.116 --> 00:06:08.993
